### ‚ö† BREAKING CHANGES

* üß® The scope for If Design System npm packages has now changed from
  `@if-design-system` to `@ids-core`. We have also renamed the repository
  from `if-design-system` to `ids-core`
* üß® The Social icons category is now removed, it has been replaced by SoMe
* üß® faq icon renamed to faq-bubble
* üß® Util is now renamed to Utils
* üß® We have now changed the navigation structure for the documentation site.
  Please update any saved links!
* üß® Navigation structure has now changed. Please see release notes!
